Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
Section 11: Connection to Omega16 and the Cl(4,4) Complex Structure\
\>", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"a535792c-1831-4aaa-9c2e-175149c7318a"],

Cell["\<\
The Clifford algebra Cl(4,4) package defines the 16x16 complex structure \
matrix Omega16 (the ambient complex structure on the full 16-component spinor \
space). Similarly, Omega8 is the 8x8 complex structure on each chiral half.

The almost-complex structure J on sixPlaneAlpha is the restriction of Omega16 \
(or Omega8) to the 6-dimensional intersection:

  J = i_sixPlane^* Omega8  (pullback of Omega8 to sixPlaneAlpha)

where i_sixPlane: sixPlaneAlpha -> R^8 is the inclusion. This means J is not \
arbitrary but is canonically induced by the ambient Clifford-algebra complex \
structure.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"b01bf463-4695-45b9-8f5f-2e8f4dd74cd6"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
(* ---- Connect J to Omega8 from Dirac-Lord-Nash_4+4.wl ---- *)

(* Omega8 is available from the loaded package: DiracLordNash44`Omega8 *)
(* (If the package is loaded, Omega8 = sigma8 . Q[7]) *)

(* Pullback of Omega8 to sixPlaneAlpha via basis matrix B (6x8) *)
(* J_induced = B . Omega8 . Transpose[B] (using g6=Id as metric on sixPlane) *)
(* Note: B is the 6x8 basis matrix computed in Section 2 *)

If[ValueQ[DiracLordNash44`Omega8],
  Omega8package = DiracLordNash44`Omega8;
  Print[\"Omega8 from package loaded successfully.\"];
  Jpullback = B . Omega8package . Transpose[B];
  Print[\"Pullback of Omega8 to sixPlaneAlpha:\"];
  Print[MatrixForm[Chop[Jpullback]]];
  Print[\"J_pullback^2 = -Identity: \",
    If[Chop[Jpullback.Jpullback + IdentityMatrix[6]] == 0*IdentityMatrix[6], \
\"VERIFIED\", \"NOT verified (check basis normalization)\"]];
,
  Print[\"(Package Omega8 not available in current context - using abstract \
J6 defined in Section 5)\"];
  Print[\"To use the Cl(4,4) connection, evaluate Section 0 first to load the \
package.\"];
];\
\>", "Input",
 CellLabel->
  "In[530]:=",ExpressionUUID->"7b7a23da-b930-453c-bc57-d1a7cd2020de"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

